# Stone Paper Scissors Game Using HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Stone Paper Scissors (also called Rock Paper Scissors) is a simple hand game usually played between two people.
Each player randomly chooses one of three things:

* Stone (Rock) 🪨
* Paper 📄
* Scissors ✂️

Rules:

* Stone beats Scissors (Stone   crushes Scissors)
* Scissors beats Paper (Scissors cut Paper)
* Paper beats Stone (Paper covers Stone)

If both players choose the same thing, it’s a draw!